data.description: Don't miss out on this ranch-style home that sits on a beautiful 4.6 acre lot, and is only minutes from Jackson Lake!!! This parcel is sold together with 61 Conley Ditch Rd., which is the 2 acre parcel to the right (55 Conley Ditch Rd has 2.6 acres, for a total of 4.6 acres). The house offers a split bedroom plan, a great room, and a spacious kitchen with breakfast area. It has a nice covered front porch, covered deck, a long driveway, lots of parking to accommodate cars, RVs and other toys, and a nice, flat private yard with beautiful trees away from main road. Bring your creativity and care and make this property your own dream home! The possibilities are endless!!!
